          <h2>Why eat local</h2>
          <p>Food businesses jeopardize the quality of food by overusing chemicals in order 
to mass produce the food and shorten the reach-to-market time, also the safety of food reaching 
from inventories located hundreds of miles away from store is also another point to peruse. </p>
          <h2>Farmers</h2>
